cc:Work.dc:title: Flower of Life Symbol
cc:Work.dc:description: The Flower of Life symbol is claimed to be one of the most powerful esoteric symbols with first useage dating back hundreds of thousands of years (an alternate history is also proposed in which human civilization existed then as well.) The symbol has been popularized by Drunvalo Melchizedek. This rendering is hand-drawn in a vector illustrator program and hence not completely precise, but has proven very effective for me as a calming device.
